    <item>
      <title>[입에 착착 붙는 일본어] (못을 박은 듯이) 꼼짝 못하게 되다</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/nie/japanese/2025/06/13/SAINN7T3MJGPTFWZC45T23VIM4/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/nie/japanese/2025/06/13/SAINN7T3MJGPTFWZC45T23VIM4/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
